{"tid":1214910,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"六月飛煙","createTime":"2019-06-13T05:36:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T13:50:36.000Z","uid":234351,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4274f3c51a020390301ddf8fa607abcfe0bfde9c","tid":1214910,"uid":234351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:36:03.000Z","msg":"發夢食完煙有感<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇乜對過音歡迎集思廣益<br />\n巴打絲打有其他歌提議都可以講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n當 在我活著熟悉的小都市竟忽爾變天<br />\n預見自在樂土即將不見<br />\n才會站上前 拼命上前<br />\n送中 話我白白幻想擔心修法返不了昨天<br />\n話我沒犯罪怎想到寬免 誰奮力詐騙<br />\n一送中 掛念往日數十年（明日還望誰倖免）<br />\n一送中 說話亦會惹禍延 狀況會蔓延<br />\n無話再講只得再問天 誰明白這件事<br />\n<br />\n六月飛煙 個個痛哭哽咽 誰又會理會誰發言<br />\n率先印證了夢魘<br />\n限時盡了 剩下烽煙 往四周躲閃<br />\n人人呼吸都似試煉<br />\n誰夠膽去欺騙再等十年<br />\n<br />\n當 又再聚集大家終點一致都不怕開片<br />\n又到十字路口搶先攻佔<br />\n列隊也不易 再度上前<br />\n不要等 掛念往日數十年（明日還望誰倖免）<br />\n不要等 注定像抱病自憐 在仰天祭奠<br />\n忘掉野史改變歷史 齊成就這義事<br />\n<br />\n六月飛煙 個個痛哭哽咽 誰又會理會誰發言<br />\n率先印證了夢魘<br />\n限時盡了 剩下烽煙 往四周躲閃<br />\n人人呼吸都似試煉<br />\n誰夠膽去欺騙再等十年<br />\n<br />\n即使你將我欺壓已數十年<br />\n槍都開將理想鎮壓 誰未發現<br />\n開天闢地今天 一起聚集 沒下次<br />\n人人同祈望基督今晚蒞臨<br />\n為何無行動也恐怕不治 怎去醫<br />\n齊成就這義事 齊懷著信念<br />\n<br />\n六月飛煙 怨氣也都沖天 還是會決定來發言<br />\n奢想抗拒這夢魘<br />\n淚流盡了 剩下烽煙 法哪可彰顯<br />\n人人不敢講天天卻無眠<br />\n誰夠膽去欺騙再等十年<br />\n明明一雙手不算得刀劍<br />\n誰始終向善<br />\n<br />\n最兇惡的 笑亦泰然<br />\n最驚怕的 喊亦泰然<br />\n送中哪可 送亦泰然"},{"pid":"38813f9ca1e2f3f1a58bea3c1d4f7bfa7dba7e36","tid":1214910,"uid":234351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:32:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae16a5a7ee7353762b17f801e4040ef93538843","tid":1214910,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T07:36:41.000Z","msg":"push 文宣"},{"pid":"76c06077d2fd87c1f943ef97ad2b241d431c07ff","tid":1214910,"uid":234351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T08:39:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba2b74a5dc3b1fe7cd8c4009a284d34a20b0f4a","tid":1214910,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221e8b427270ebdf00f2a7d9061252c7417e69c6","tid":1214910,"uid":234351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eba2b74a5dc3b1fe7cd8c4009a284d34a20b0f4a","tid":1214910,"uid":86723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd880af2443b3e4ddde410576a6eb3a63d8c928a","tid":1214910,"uid":175750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afe3a5f45cbb3dda54f2085661537567aee148f5","tid":1214910,"uid":234351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd880af2443b3e4ddde410576a6eb3a63d8c928a","tid":1214910,"uid":175750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T10:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:39:57.000Z","m